title: BRIEF-AB Announces February 28 2018 Assets Under Management
text: March 12, 2018 / 8:21 PM / Updated 13 minutes ago BRIEF-AB Announces February 28 2018 Assets Under Management Reuters Staff March 12 (Reuters) - Alliancebernstein Holding Lp: * AB ANNOUNCES FEBRUARY 28, 2018 ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT * ALLIANCEBERNSTEIN HOLDING LP - ‍PRELIMINARY ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT DECREASED TO $555 BILLION DURING FEBRUARY 2018 FROM $569 BILLION AT END OF JANUARY​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Brief@thomsonreuters.com)
